   discover our current campaigns

   Future of Waste_Energies for Climate_Fair Wear_Refugees…
   let's go !

   HORiZONS : Waynak (Where are you?) is the first webdoc that lets you
   discover and collaborate with social entrepreneurs in the Near East and
   Europe, currently developing short, middle and long term solutions to
   impact the Refugees ‘Crisis’. In November 2016, meet social
   entrepreneurs from Lebanon, Jordan, Turkey, Greece, France, Germany,
   United Kingdom and more… and help them solve their challenges.
   Discover

   You are a social entrepreneur ?
   Join our incubator

   #join makesense in your city

   Discover the MakeSense Chapters Map and find the closest Chapter near
   you

   Can’t find a MakeSense Chapter near your city and you want to kickstart
   one? Get in touch with the Community Development team! We will send you
   more information about the next MakeSense Kickstarter Program
   (three-month online program to kickstart MakeSense in your city)

